name: Ben Brown
text: Very dissatisfied with our 2 large pizzas 1 large cinnamon dessert and a ham cheese sub. A lot of food and none of it actually  close to even being good. Trying to buy local and support my area but this was ridiculous.  Usually the food is really good but not this evening. Very disappointed .

text: Eat here probably twice a month or more. My kids absolutely love their pizza. Wings are delicious and my favorite. Less than $1 a wing so better than most places.
